\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔病多幾年先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1696de0c18b49d0782caa1ce3b6cbd7dfd0dde5","tid":910911,"uid":63909,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"da9a236d9b418a54113d164e12940435d7764c5c","tid":910911,"uid":157362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"051d577bc314ec60752e8a3375d63c434245261e","tid":910911,"uid":35776,"like":128,"dislike":1,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"本報獲悉，今年6月獲全國人大常委會續任基本法委員會港方委員的劉迺強去世，終年71歲。劉迺強認識多年的港區人大代表蔡素玉向《明報》證實消息，她向本報表示，劉迺強患癌症多年，經歷多次手術和化療，形容消息「既突然又不突然」，透露數星期前曾與對方見面，「一齊飲茶」，當時對方剛做完手術不久，身體較弱，但仍關心社會大事，<span style=\"color: red;\">又思考如何幫助年輕人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00001/1542806013919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F1542806013919&d=BxbtS97f2HqX%2BhpLIkm3qcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=fdf41a0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181121%2Fs00001%2F1542806013919&h=dae4fdfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181121/s00001/1542806013919</a><br />\n<br />\n坐言起行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67906409c0f4c2ac8576bb56d350c44f235ed6ab","tid":910911,"uid":33799,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:47:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181121/58941760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181121%2F58941760&d=BxbtS97f2HqX%2BhpLIkm3qcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0993cfeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181121%2F58941760&h=e4962b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181121/58941760</a><br />\n<br />\n上世紀80年代創立首批民主派政團匯點、倡議「民主回歸」的香港基本法委員會委員劉迺強今晚病逝，終年71歲。前立法會議員、民建聯蔡素玉接受《蘋果》查詢時證實，獲劉迺強友人告知，劉今晚病逝。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蔡素玉指，劉迺強患癌「病咗好耐」，「上次話我哋聽，做咗7、8次化療，又要做手術」，指約三星期前曾與他見面，「當時覺得佢面色差，但仲好樂觀喎，講嘢都登登聲（即大聲），好掛住政事，成日寫網誌，又傳啲文章畀我哋睇」；及至上星期，他未能出席另一次朋友聚會。</span><br />\n<br />\n蔡說劉勇敢面對病魔，「（病情）咁多年惡化、施手術都無數，但佢都好勇敢面對」。對其突然離世感到突然，讚揚對方多年來一直關心香港問題，「對香港好有心」。<br />\n2016年全國人大常委會委員長張德江於政府總部會見香港各界人士時，原本站着聽講的劉迺強身體不適，張即着職員找椅子讓劉坐下，更對自己的話太長表示抱歉。張的發言多次因此被打斷，先後慰問劉「沒問題吧？」最終劉在張的發言尾聲由救護員送離現場，張則向劉揮手道別，並叫在場人士掌聲鼓勵身體不適的劉迺強"},{"pid":"6b93d9aa4846c9624b323947fc07e0652891fd7f","tid":910911,"uid":39181,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"竟然睇唔到中國點贏美國就瓜左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e045a0444efb4a98780a0a70f653e7b